{"tid":1517022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白色恐怖真係黎得好快 就黎抖唔到氣  圍爐區","createTime":"2019-08-29T19:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T00:10:03.000Z","uid":30910,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"63937e624c66720dca489b62dfdde8dbb8baade7","tid":1517022,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:02:26.000Z","msg":"起我底都知我幫太古打工<br />\n雖然唔係國泰 但係你真係唔知幾時燒到埋身<br />\n今日突然 覺得自己係FB講左咁多野<br />\n成日屌鬼屌政府 好似好危險咁<br />\n再加上依家成條狗鐵加上通街都係CCTV<br />\n突然有一種抖唔到氣既感覺<br />\n好恐怖 以前就笑大陸狗<br />\n估唔到自己有生之年都會經歷到依種<br />\n有話說不得既感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講出黎都係希望大家可以同我圍爐下<br />\n互相支持下<br />\n同埋大家都唔好怕係FB上面講<br />\n營造一個大既氣氛<br />\n唔好被依種白色恐怖收我地皮<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n我地加油"},{"pid":"31a028f086a8911910ad541c83cce1b0efd00a87","tid":1517022,"uid":65380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:03:20.000Z","msg":"香港人齊上齊落，巴打加油"},{"pid":"0fb50d02119f6c912f652110963f8f1a9521514d","tid":1517022,"uid":256594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"唔驚，仲有我哋嚟同你一齊渡過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74169aca5b133f905436ecf643fa590f1d49f829","tid":1517022,"uid":87189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:05:15.000Z","msg":"巴打支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d89b61a6608cdab68be27374b57375b0518b9fa","tid":1517022,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:05:29.000Z","msg":"共產黨係真實"},{"pid":"8c11e29819164b6eb7f21b309d68c68b80d6760e","tid":1517022,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:05:59.000Z","msg":"等到10月底"},{"pid":"cd6f8c0ebcad81c521925c8b80c6b085e9d493d9","tid":1517022,"uid":60790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T19:06:26.000Z","msg":"仲讀緊書未出黎做野 <br />\n但生活係白色恐怖之下真係好辛苦 不知不覺間著衫著咩色會諗 自